## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the potential bias in sources. The complexity of the issue means that perspectives can vary widely based on political, economic, and social viewpoints. Additionally, the report relies on secondary sources, which may not capture the full scope of the private prison industry's impact. Further research, including empirical studies and firsthand accounts, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the issue.